Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是魔族登錄證？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,監測魔族身體狀態的簡易回路被植入了遲效性病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是昨天駭入特區警備隊網路的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Island Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,被擺一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,犯人的真正目的並非劫持總部的伺服器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而是這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有別的辦法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,手鐲和特區警備隊的網路並不相連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(497.333,980)}魔族登錄證
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(818.667,980)}Island Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也沒有物理路徑可以傳送掃毒程式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1421.333,980)}疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 小姐妳應該有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在魔族登錄證獨立運作模式下的強行介入辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對了...還可以靠「C」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以淺蔥才會被找上來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能解決這次事件的只有妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去基石之門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼抱怨之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然 今天真的會是絃神島的末日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂...饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,學長...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,妳那是什麼臉啊 姬柊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經昏迷一小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時？有這麼短嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是做了相當長的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 奧蘿菈...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那個應該不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,古城小哥 你總算醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,摩怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你可沒有時間慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快點看看市區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這是深淵之陷搞的鬼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他們用病毒劫持了魔族登錄證
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正在汲取魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,薔薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那是魔法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,密度高得難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是深淵薔薇的真面目嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐為了解除這狀況正趕向基石之門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,古城小哥 能請你在她解決前先防止絃神島完蛋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不會再讓你為所欲為了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,迅即到來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,獅子之黃金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Regulus Aurum
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,復活了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那個「薔薇」的召喚魔法仍在持續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,迅即到來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,龍蛇之水銀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Al Meissa Mercury
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊 抱歉 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是做了身為監視者該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 再這樣下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白 城市撐不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,六式重裝降魔弓？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(924,980)}Der Freiscütz
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,多重魔彈鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Multi Lockon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這術式該不會是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,古城！雪菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,唯里！志緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還有煌坂...葛蓮妲也來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,妲～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只要找出那魔法陣的施術者就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,辦得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對舞威媛來說這可是基本中的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,撼鳴吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,認證申請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,六式降魔弓．改 原Ⅲ 解鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(885,980)}Freikugel Plus Proto Ⅲ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1316,980)}Unlock
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,六式降魔劍．改 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(873.333,980)}Rosenkavalier Plus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1225.333,980)}Boot up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,古城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊就交給我們 你先休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,學長...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些話想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊 為什麼把我帶來這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是你可以吸我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要讓我自己說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了讓狄珊珀支配眷獸的能力失效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,假如我猜想的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只要學長身為吸血鬼的能力變強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就不會被奪走眷獸的支配權
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我這樣...不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...也不是不行的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在這種狀況下...我有點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼學長 請閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊 這是...？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因為用手帕長度不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是手帕？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有股香味耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,類似肥皂...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要聞 也不必解說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得...怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但我會希望能一直這樣摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,別摸...很癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,學、學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣...不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請你多吸一點...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 姬柊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再繼續下去妳的身體會...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...照現在這樣或許還贏不了狄珊珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,妲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 葛蓮妲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,唯里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,葛蓮妲累了 所以我想帶她跟你們一起休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有看見...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,古、古城？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,葛蓮妲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 因為情況緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這次就破例准許你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,僅限這次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小、小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說准什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等、等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我不排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我是第一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩妳忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別看我 小雪
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TITLE----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.96,title1,,0,0,0,,{\be25\pos(960,800)\fad(583,0)}深淵的薔薇篇Ⅲ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TITLE----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,煌華麟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,煌坂 咒箭還剩下多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,含備用剩下六支
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,妳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我這裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,照這樣來看頂多再撐三到四分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,斐川志緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,雙角之深緋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Alnasl Minium
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,曉古城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,紗矢華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉煌坂 我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,羽波唯里 雪菜妳也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們臉好紅 不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,曉古城 你該不會又...！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,四聖獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,司掌天上四方的四頭幻獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被視為風水術中的力量象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,利用絃神島的構造讓那四神具現成形了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是深淵之陷的壓軸王牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,找到施術者了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,三點鐘方向 距離六千兩百！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,距離六千兩百...在海上？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,絃神島第27號廢棄區塊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,九個月前才沉到海底的初期人工島舊址
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 他們最後的立足點只能在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,做好覺悟了吧 斐川志緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我才要問妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,由我們爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你們快點行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,葛蓮妲 拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 基石之門就在面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再往前就沒有掩護了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,需要支援嗎？卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊 已唾手可得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那就只好賭一賭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我先當誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妳全速跑到基石之門內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間考慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,摩怪 麻煩你支援淺蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咯咯 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,倒數要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,別想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大氣精靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(925.333,980)}Air-Elemental
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 生靈嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(943,980)}Wraith
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那招要是摧毀分身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,施術者應該也會受到相應的傷勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一來...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 狄珊珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我...在這種地方失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看來這次藥量實在重了點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的交給你了 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼了卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你走不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,抵抗無用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧 千賀毅人的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,程式「深淵薔薇」的網路佔有率下降至77％
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,目前已失去4800個魔族登錄證的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,居然連妳都攔不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,藍羽淺蔥真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭 已經夠了 妳快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的靠我來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺...好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,對方是掌握這整座人工島的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是...「C」的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好美...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不可以去 蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,卡莉、洛基...還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭的腦袋裡裝了比常人精細十六倍的神經回路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,當然活人是不可能處理的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因此她被賦予了靠死靈魔法活動的死者肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(994,980)}Necromancy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而她卻希望毀滅自己長大的故鄉「魔族特區」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,會是件奇怪的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼想 曉古城？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的憤怒或許都有正當的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像千賀說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這座島會製造出大量的犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 和你們想摧毀絃神島一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想保護在這座島上生活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要阻止你們深淵之陷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 就是屬於我的戰鬥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1155.333,980)}第四真祖的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的那套道理我不認同！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1103,980)}戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,基、基本上 還有我們在喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,妲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了 狄珊珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完喔 曉古城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,迅即到來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,摩羯之瞳晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Dabih Kryastalos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,第四真祖的眷獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我早該發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,狄珊珀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}December
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在古羅馬文明中可解作第十個月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,第十號「焰光夜伯」...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1010,980)}Kaleido Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妳和奧蘿菈一樣 是第四真祖的封印體對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,狄珊珀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非你想起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,曉古城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 9個月前的焰光之宴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,還有奧蘿菈...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妳並沒有參與那次的事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,當時我被第三真祖抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第三真祖？混沌皇女？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1102,980)}Chaos Bride
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她對你似乎相當感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,之所以釋放我 也是因為我說要來絃神島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的身體...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,「被編號」的我們本身就是第四真祖的眷獸封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(390,980)}Numbered
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,封印一解 就只有消滅的份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我所封印 同時也代表我本身的第十號眷獸──
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,摩羯之瞳晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Dabih Kryastalos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,司掌吸血鬼「魅惑」能力的眷獸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我也能辦到這種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算薔薇凋謝 召喚出來的四聖獸依然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的同伴所召換出的 摧毀絃神島的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,迅即到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,甲殼之銀霧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Natra Cinereus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,六式降魔劍．改
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Rosenkavalier Plus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,迅即到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雙角之深緋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Alnasl Minium
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,龍蛇之水銀！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(923,980)}Al Meissa Mercury
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,繼承焰光夜伯血脈之人 曉古城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(764,980)}Kaleido Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在此解放汝的伽鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,狻猊之神子暨高神劍巫於此祀求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,破魔的曙光 雪霞的神狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,速以鋼之神威助我伐滅惡神百鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,迅即到來 第五眷獸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,獅子之黃金！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(923,980)}Regulus Aurum
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是你贏了...古城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,狄珊珀...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,最後我有事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩你帶蘭...還有卡莉和洛基他們到正當的研究機構
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去那些孩子活不了多久的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 曉古城
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第十號眷獸的力量交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 狄珊珀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不用露出那麼哀傷的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 因為我會一直留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,保護好第十二號的奧蘿菈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因為她是...你的希望
